front.title: •Dark Deal
front.gametext: Deploy on Bespin: Cloud City if you control that sector and at least three related sites. At each Cloud City site, your total power is +4 and your Force drains are +2. Effect canceled if opponent occupies four Bespin locations. (Immune to Alter.)
front.lore: 'Perhaps you think you're being treated unfairly?' 'No.' 'Good. It would be unfortunate if I had to leave a garrison here.'
